window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Where do I begin? Oh. Yeah. Once upon a time. Isn’t that how all good fairy tales start?</b> </p> <p>And Maximo and I, we were definitely a fairy tale. Not the cleaned-up, sanitized ones where life’s problems are solved with a smile and a song. We were the old-school kind. </p> <p><b>A twisted tale packed with murder, violence, and a tragic beginning</b>. </p> <p>Okay, so maybe we weren’t a traditional fairy tale. After all, Maximo was more villain than prince. He was scarily sexy. Devilishly charming. Controlling, possessive, and dangerous. Especially when it came to me.<i> His</i> little dove. And heaven help anyone who tried to free me from my gilded cage.</p> <p><i>This slow burn romance features graphic language, sex, violence, and a daddy obsessed with his little dove. If this doesn't sound like your kind of fairy tale, this may not be the book for you.</i> </p>"; 
